<unit id="3feae4cb-9736-4c5a-adde-01555388b8bd">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 6</note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>This add-on is used to activate or deactivate profiles deppending on the state of browse mode.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="809c3b62-2d95-4a66-9582-4ee2ce5854cf">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 8</note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Currently, when browse mode is active, a profile named browseMode will be activated, and it will be deactivated when browse mode becomes inactive.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="82b444c0-aac7-4578-9d6d-40b1a2b7779e">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 10</note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>The browseMode profile will be automatically created if it doesn't exist.</source>
</segment>
